low-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 6px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 1.6px; line-height: 1.8; color: rgb(83, 83, 83); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong><span style="font-size: x-small;">一、文章题目</span></strong></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">文章题目字数不超过20个字。</span></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong><span style="font-size: x-small;">二、署名方式</span></strong></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">1．作者同属一个单位</span></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">李白，杜甫,白居易</span></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">（《中国交通信息化》杂志社，北京，100101）</span></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">&nbsp;2．作者分属不同单位</span></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">李白<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><sup style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">1</span></sup></span>，杜甫<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><sup style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">2</span></sup></span>，白居易<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><sup style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">1</span></sup></span>, 王维<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><sup style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">2</span></sup></span></span></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">（1．《中国交通信息化》杂志社，北京，100101；2．《中国公路》杂志社，北京，100073）</span></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong><span style="font-size: x-small;">三、作者信息</span></strong></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">论文应在文尾附上作者姓名、性别、职称、学历、单位、地址、邮编、电话及电子信箱等信息，以便责编与作者沟通和邮寄样刊使用。</span></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong><span style="font-size: x-small;">四、摘要和关键词</span></strong></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">1．中文摘要300字以内，包括研究目的、方法、结果、结论；</span></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">&nbsp;2．关键词根据需要列出。</span></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong><span style="font-size: x-small;">五、中图分类号及基金项目信息</span></strong></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">如果文章有中图分类号及基金项目信息请列出。</span></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong><span style="font-size: x-small;">六、参考文献</span></strong></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">参考文献放文尾。</span></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong><span style="font-size: x-small;">七、正文格式</span></strong></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">1．论文标题居中，小二号宋体，加粗，单倍行距。</span></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">2．作者单位、姓名居中，五号宋体，单倍行距。署名方式见上。</span></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">3．摘要及关键词小五号宋体，单倍行距，居左空两格。</span></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">4．正文采用正文格式，五号宋体，单倍行距，全文不分栏。</span></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">5．一级标题用一，二，三，…表示，小四号宋体加粗；二级标题用（一），（二），（三），…表示，五号宋体加粗；三级标题用 1，2，3表示，五号宋体，层次标题以下，还可使用（1），（2），（3），…；再以下，使用①，②，③，…五号宋体；段落标题均为正文格式，居左空两格。</span></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: x-small;">6．文中图片、表格、引文、公式、定理等的序号，均按其在正文中被引用的顺序统一用阿拉伯数字顺序编码。</span></section></section></section><section style="margin: 5px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(202, 29, 24); height: 1px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></section></section><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; text-indent: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: right; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p></section><p><br/></p>'
